- in conf file, modify HOME to set your home directory

- copy conf file in /etc/init/ dir:
sudo cp ./daemon/express-chat.conf /etc/init/

- add permissions for your user
sudo chown tug /etc/init/express-chat.conf

- run:
start express-chat

- stop:
stop express-chat

---> from http://kevin.vanzonneveld.net/techblog/article/run_nodejs_as_a_service_on_ubuntu_karmic/

